.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, tram, train, taxi
The people have 5 different jobs:  electrician, security-guard, photographer, designer, manager
5 different games are played: canasta, go, chess, billiard, backgammon
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, cycling, soccer, volleyball, rowing

1. the electrician is the person driving the boat
2. the security-guard is the person who's sport is rugby
3. the person drinking coffee is the person driving the quad-bike
4. the photographer is the person drinking tea
5. the person driving the quad-bike is to the right of the person driving the tram
6. the person playing canasta is the person who's sport is rowing
7. the person playing go is the person driving the train
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the designer is on the far left
10. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling
11. the person playing go is to the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball
12. the person playing billiard is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the manager is the person playing backgammon
14. the designer is to the left or right of the person driving the taxi

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Job	|   designer	|    photographer	|     electrician	|    security-guard	|    manager	|
| Transport		|    train	|      taxi	|      boat	|     tram	|     quad-bike	|
| Beverage	|     water	|      tea	|      milk	| orange-juice	|     coffee	|
| Game		|     go	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| billiard	|   parliament	|
| Sport		|     cycling	|     volleyball	|     rowing	|     rugby	|     soccer	|
